{"tid":1694341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好將區議會送俾建制，唔好將連登送俾狗","createTime":"2019-11-05T06:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T08:13:22.000Z","uid":303750,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1993b0f0428f64a44a379275823657f400e7ff97","tid":1694341,"uid":303750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:09:39.000Z","msg":"你唔投票，就係將區議會送俾建制<br />\n<br />\n你唔留言，就係將連登送俾風向狗<br />\n<br />\n今日香港變成咁<br />\n有一半係我呢種港豬自作自受<br />\n<br />\n我地既網絡禮儀就係兄弟爬山<br />\n不分化不割蓆不篤灰不譴責<br />\n你愈肯拎空閒時間俾心機討論，愈容易拎到共識<br />\n講歪理既人就帶唔到風向<br />\n<br />\n起底要做，但起底只能做一半參考<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家手閒果陣摺一兩隻紙鶴祈禱周同學轉好 <br />\n宗教上有用，心理上都有用"},{"pid":"20a43923e4bfd510e5d3b3aa7fa79f6b4684e576","tid":1694341,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:15:57.000Z","msg":"選舉近了。&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;飯民開始上水了"},{"pid":"0e7be583cd2a3e79cd4d7945ca751b56e46e4db0","tid":1694341,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"講得好岩，大家加油"},{"pid":"242077b6c0db9724c0b2b7c064dd74ab56da1cd5","tid":1694341,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ce131392ef3c0581afc07ea157ca1fda6d8ce1","tid":1694341,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:54:37.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1fd2786101b2dc2ec717631d272468f5a1859372","tid":1694341,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb5d0a5ae30acd40fc4575ebaabe1ae686b6db5","tid":16